
@{
    Layout = null;
}

<div class="caption">
    <i class="icon-settings font-green"></i>
    <span class="caption-subject font-green sbold uppercase">Evaluation Criteria</span>
</div>
<p>Kindly take note of the following:
    1. The evaluation of all tender responses shall be based on weighted average scoring of technical & financial proposals.
    2. Preliminary evaluation, technical evaluation and financial evaluation shall strictly be done as per the guidelines provided
    in the Public Procurement & Assets Disposal Act (PPADA).
    3. Unless stated otherwise, the default bid selection method applicable to this Tender shall be the Quality and Cost Based
    Selection method (QCBS).</p>

<table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover table-responsive" id="tbl_eval_criteria">
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>Template ID</th>
        <th>Description</th>
        <th>Total Preliminary (Mandatory) Checkscore</th>
        <th>Total Technical Evaluation Score %</th>
        <th>Total Financial Evaluation Score %</th>
        <th>Total Weighted Score</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody></tbody>
</table>


